---
    import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
    ---

    <Layout title="Join Our Volunteer Team!">
      <main>
        <section class="hero">
          <h1>Namaskar!</h1>
          <p>We’re seeking passionate and innovative individuals like you to join our team of volunteers. We believe that collaboration and knowledge sharing are crucial to advancing our efforts in using technology to spread the Nama of Ma Adya Kali across the interwebs – a truly impactful mission.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="looking-for">
          <h2>Are You Ready to Make a Difference?</h2>
          <h3>We’re Looking For:</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Tech Enthusiasts:</strong> Anyone with experience in IT, Computer Science, or tech-related fields – from web development to cybersecurity – is welcome to contribute!</li>
            <li><strong>Curious Learners:</strong> We’re passionate about exploring new technologies! Think Python, web development, cybersecurity, or anything that sparks your curiosity and desire to learn.</li>
            <li><strong>Hands-On Builders:</strong> Do you love building things from scratch? We want to help you dive into hands-on projects and develop valuable new skills.</li>
            <li><strong>Creative Problem-Solvers:</strong> You’re comfortable tackling challenges, troubleshooting, and learning as you go – we need someone ready to roll up your sleeves and find solutions.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="what-we-value">
          <h2>What We Value in Our Volunteers:</h2>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Self-Driven Initiative:</strong> We really value individuals who are comfortable working independently, proactively troubleshooting, and continuously learning. Don’t worry about having all the answers – we’ll be there to guide and support you.</li>
            <li><strong>Embracing Growth Through Challenges:</strong> We understand that learning often involves making mistakes. We want to see you embrace those moments as opportunities to grow and refine your approach. It’s okay to stumble – the key is to learn from it!</li>
            <li><strong>Ownership & Proactive Engagement:</strong> We want to see someone who takes ownership of their learning journey and actively seeks out opportunities to grow and contribute.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="skills-shine">
          <h2>Where Your Skills Can Shine:</h2>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Python & Scripting:</strong> Developing and maintaining scripts for automation – streamlining processes and improving efficiency.</li>
            <li><strong>Other Automation Languages & Frameworks:</strong> Developing and maintaining scripts for automation – streamlining processes and improving efficiency.</li>
            <li><strong>AI & Machine Learning:</strong> Exploring and experimenting with AI tools and techniques, including image AI and training models for creative applications.</li>
            <li><strong>ChatGPT & Large Language Models:</strong> Utilizing and experimenting with ChatGPT and other large language models for various applications.</li>
            <li><strong>Chatbot Development:</strong> Designing and building conversational AI interfaces.</li>
          </ul>
          <p>We encourage volunteers to propose innovative automation solutions and to bring your own ideas to the table – let’s build something amazing together!</p>
          <p>Interested? Please fill out <a href="https://forms.gle/q8VUeweHReUMBNgg9">this form</a>.</p>
        </section>
      </main>
      <footer style="text-align: center;">
        Made with Love by AI using Bolt.diy ❤️
      </footer>
    </Layout>

    <style>
      main {
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 2rem;
        max-width: 960px;
        font-family: sans-serif;
        color: #f0f0f0;
      }

      section {
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
      }

      h1, h2, h3 {
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #b00000;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        text-align: center;
      }

      h2 {
        font-size: 2rem;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #4a4a4a;
        padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
      }

      h3 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
      }

      ul {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
      }

      li {
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        line-height: 1.4;
      }

      strong {
        color: #a3b18a;
      }

      p {
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      /* Responsive Design */
      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        main {
          padding: 1rem;
        }

        h1 {
          font-size: 2rem;
        }

        h2 {
          font-size: 1.75rem;
        }

        h3 {
          font-size: 1.25rem;
        }
      }

      /* Minimalist Design Aesthetic */
      body {
        background-color: #000000;
        color: #f0f0f0;
        background-image: url('kali.png'); /* Path to your image */
        background-size: cover; /* Cover the entire background */
        background-repeat: no-repeat; /* Do not repeat the image */
        background-attachment: fixed; /* Fixed position to prevent scrolling with content */
      }

      /* Subtle Futuristic Elements */
      h1, h2, h3, p, li {
        text-shadow: 0.5px 0.5px 0 #000;
      }

      .made-with-love {
        text-align: center;
      }
    </style>
